  "source_code": "#include<stdio.h>\nint main()\n{\n\tlong long int a,b;\n\tscanf(\"%lld %lld\",&a,&b);\n\twhile((a!=0)&&(b!=0))\n\t{\n\t\tif(a>=2*b)\n\t\t{\n\t\t\ta=a%(2*b);\n\t\t}\n\t\telse if(b>=2*a)\n\t\t{\n\t\t\tb=b%(2*a);\n\t\t}\n\t\telse\n\t\t{\n\t\t\tbreak;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\tprintf(\"%lld %lld\",a,b);\n\treturn 0;\n}\n\t\t\n\t\n",
